  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;Asset Owners Disclosure Project works to educate long-term investors about their carbon risk. The goal of the Environmental Ratings Project is to shift investment behavior from the short to long term, which will result in more investments that achieve positive environmental impacts. This goal will be achieved by compiling and disseminating information about how institutional investors are managing their climate risk, showing the leaders and laggards. The index creates peer pressure for funds to improve, resulting in less carbon-intensive investments.&quot;</narrative>
  </description>
